data.description: Seller willing to finance!! Beautiful West Valley manufactured home is now available! Come and see this spacious 3 bedroom 2 bath gem situated on a 1/2 acre. Freshly painted inside and out. With gorgeous hardwood floors throughout! Spacious primary suite complete with dual sinks and walk-in closet. A new front deck with plenty of room to relax on. Beautiful and open kitchen, family room and great room space. Plenty of off-street parking with enough space to add a shop. If this looks like it checks all the right boxes, call your favorite Realtor today and schedule a tour!
